data.text:
Are you on a mission to photograph or write about any of this summer’s events? Accreditation can only be applied for through this form and should be done as soon as possible, no later than 2 days before the concert date. Late applications will not be accepted.

If there are multiple writers/photographers from the same publication, please coordinate internally before submitting your application. We only approve one writer and one photographer per publication.
